6 defined in 75-6-304.
7 (c) "Montana coal endowment fund" means the coal severance tax infrastructure endowment fund
8 established in 17-5-703(1)(b).
9 (d) "Montana coal endowment program" means the local government infrastructure investment
10 program established in subsection (1).
11 (e) "Public swimming pool" has the meaning provided in 50-53-102.
12 (e)(f) "Tribal government" means a federally recognized Indian tribe within the state of Montana."
